  <original-body>Currently, calling reload on a model does not clear the attribute changes:

@@@ ruby
product.name = &quot;foo&quot;
product.changed? # =&gt; true
product.reload
product.changed? # =&gt; true
@@@

This patch fixes this problem by clearing the changed attributes after a reload. Tests are included.</original-body>
